# Share Profile Modal - Nakul Uppal

A stylish, responsive profile card featuring a modal popup with social media share buttons. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The UI includes smooth animations, gradients, and a clean layout for an engaging user experience.

---

## üì∏ Preview

The project displays:
- A personal card with photo, name, and designation
- A **"Share My Profile"** button that triggers a modal with social icons
- A **"Follow Me"** button (UI only)
- Floating animated gradient background circles

